    {\textstyle x=e_{i}P}
   is a probability vector representing the distribution of a random walker's locations after taking a single step from vertex 
  
    
      
        i
      
    
    {\textstyle i}
  ; i.e., 
  
    
      
        
          x
          
            j
          
        
